OL,3,CNew Welsh Government sets out #249m
OL,4,Cspending plans
OL,6,FThe Welsh Government has announced
OL,7,F#249 million funding for school
OL,8,Fbuildings, social housing, and
OL,9,Fhospitals.
OL,11,FThe first Supplementary Budget was
OL,12,Fpublished on Tuesday and included #20
OL,13,Fmillion for social housing, #40
OL,14,Fmillion to improve school buildings
OL,15,Fand #5 million for community
OL,16,Ffacilities.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,436,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1782238703
OL,3,CNew Welsh Government sets out #249m
OL,4,Cspending plans
OL,6,FIt also includes #10 million for bus
OL,7,Fand coach travel, #2 million for the
OL,8,FCynnal child payment and #2 million to
OL,9,Fgive more children the chance to learn
OL,10,Fto swim.
OL,12,FThis follows announcements made last
OL,13,Fweek, including #55 million being
OL,14,Fallocated to help families access
OL,15,Ffunded childcare for their two-year-
OL,16,Folds.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,436,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1782238703
OL,3,CNew Welsh Government sets out #249m
OL,4,Cspending plans
OL,6,FThe Government also confirmed a #145m
OL,7,Fboost for the NHS to help patients be
OL,8,Fseen more quickly, including #25
OL,9,Fmillion for new surgical and
OL,10,Fdiagnostic hubs to speed up cancer and
OL,11,Fdiagnostic tests and #20 million for
OL,12,Fmaintenance in hospitals and surgeries.
OL,14,FYesterday, #15 million was announced
OL,15,Fso that more secondary school pupils
OL,16,Ffrom families on Universal Credit can
OL,17,Freceive free school meals, in time for
OL,18,Fthe new term.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
