OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,436,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1782238703
OL,3,CNew Welsh Government sets out #249m
OL,4,Cspending plans
OL,6,FThe Cabinet Minister for Finance, Elin
OL,7,FJones, said: "This Supplementary
OL,8,FBudget concentrates resources on our
OL,9,Fclearest priorities: cutting NHS
OL,10,Fwaiting times, expanding childcare,
OL,11,Fextending free school meals, and
OL,12,Feasing cost-of-living pressures for
OL,13,Ffamilies."
OL,15,FShe added: "This is about more than
OL,16,Fnew funding, it's about beginning to
OL,17,Freshape how our public services work
OL,18,Fafter 27 years of a previous
OL,19,Fgovernment.
OL,26,@uD@JO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/8
